events_found.title: The San Jose Nutcracker
events_found.description: Complete your familys holiday traditions with The San Jose Nutcracker . This unique take on the classic tale of Clara and the Nutcracker is set against the backdrop of 1905 San Jose, including its famous electric tower.
events_found.address: California Theatre 345 South 1st Street, San Jose , CA 95113
